{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb68d07bb-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300ee–33"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"300ee–33"},"text":"§ 300ee–33.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Provision of information to underserved populations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb68d07bc-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300ee–33/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary may make grants to public entities, to migrant health centers (as defined in section 254b(a) ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002421"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002421"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" of this title), to community health centers (as defined in section 254c(a) "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002421"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" of this title), and to nonprofit private entities concerned with acquired immune deficiency syndrome, for the purpose of assisting grantees in providing services to populations of individuals that are underserved with respect to programs providing information on the prevention of exposure to, and the transmission of, the etiologic agent for acquired immune deficiency syndrome."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb68d07bd-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300ee–33/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Preferences in making grants","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In making grants under subsection (a), the Secretary shall give preference to any applicant for such a grant that has the ability to disseminate rapidly the information described in subsection (a) (including any national organization with such ability).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb68d07be-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1944-07-01/ch373"},"text":"July 1, 1944, ch. 373","children":[],"tail":", title XXV, formerly title XV, § 2523, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/607/tII/s221"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–607, title II, § 221","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-11-04"},"text":"Nov. 4, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/3103"},"text":"102 Stat. 3103","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered title XXV, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/93/s5/e/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–93, § 5(e)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1989-08-16"},"text":"Aug. 16, 1989","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/103/612"},"text":"103 Stat. 612","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idb68d07bf-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idb68d07c0-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idb68d07c1-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Sections 254b and 254c of this title, referred to in subsec. (a), were in the original references to sections 329 and 330, meaning sections 329 and 330 of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1944-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1944","children":[],"tail":", which were omitted in the general amendment of subpart I (§ 254b et seq.) of part D of subchapter II of this chapter by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/299/s2"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–299, § 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-10-11"},"text":"Oct. 11, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/3626"},"text":"110 Stat. 3626","children":[],"tail":". Sections 2 and 3(a) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/299"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–299","children":[],"tail":" enacted new sections 330 and 330A of act "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1944-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1944","children":[],"tail":", which are classified, respectively, to sections 254b and 254c of this title."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idb68d07c2-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idb68d07c3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Reference to Community, Migrant, Public Housing, or Homeless Health Center Considered Reference to Health Center","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Reference to community health center, migrant health center, public housing health center, or homeless health center considered reference to health center, see ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/299/s4/c"},"text":"section 4(c) of Pub. L. 104–299","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "}